Kalos Systems

$ systemsCount 0

# F12 Start/Add System
    ? systemsCount greaterThan 0
        ? systemsCount lessThan 4
            systemsCount add 1
    ? systemsCount lessThanOrEqual 0
        systemsCount subtract -1
        start

>
    at 0:50 markUrgent
    at 1:00 stop

& Systems Count Text
    type text
    value systemsCount
    position topRight